member.summary:
Parses opening and closed start tags only. It's enough to get attribute values.

  // Opening start tag
  <link rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' href='jasmine_2._0.jasmine.css'>
  // Closed start tag
  <link rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' href='jasmine_2._0.jasmine.css' />

Parser ignores attributes without values:

  // Ignores attribute 'defer'
  <script defer src="file:///D:\tests\tests.js"></script>
